# SQL Injection UNION Enumeration — Full Comment Variants

Comprehensive payload list with all comment style variants (`--`, `#`, `/**/`) where applicable.

Each block goes from 1 column up to 50 columns (NULL-padded).

Replace `TABLE_NAME_HERE` with your target table.


---


# ORACLE

> Oracle supports `--` and `/* */` comments. Does NOT support `#`.

> Always needs `FROM` clause; uses `all_tables` / `all_tab_columns`.


